Page[513]=new Array("The filter feature lets you set the filter response to stabilize noisy measurements. The 2601B-PULSE uses a digital filter, which is based on reading conversions. The displayed, stored, or transmitted reading is calculated using one or more reading conversions (from 1 to 100).","Filters","11532.htm");
