Page[524]=new Array(" ","@Carefully consider and configure the appropriate output-off state, source, and compliance limits before connecting the 2601B-PULSE to a device that can deliver energy (for example, other voltage sources, batteries, capacitors, solar cells, or other 2601B-PULSE instruments). Configure recommended instrument settings before making connections to the device. Failure to consider the output-off state, source, and compliance limits may result in damage to the instrument or to the device under test (DUT).","Output-off states","15424.htm");
