Page[536]=new Array("You can save scripts to nonvolatile memory using commands.","Only named scripts can be saved to nonvolatile memory. The anonymous script must be named before it can be saved to nonvolatile memory.","@If a script is not saved to nonvolatile memory, the script is lost when the instrument is turned off.","Save a user script","16803.htm");
